{"type":"message","id":"363a8689","parentId":"995dc77a","timestamp":"2026-05-07T04:17:16.629Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Saved successfully. Now I should reply acknowledging this. The user sent it directly to me in a Feishu DM, so I should reply in a conversational way.","thinkingSignature":"881a3bd873509e62d82f0195d8969aa02aa6338035fe6a86f404c1b9db06a5ff"},{"type":"text","text":"已存到 `notes/跨境电商起链接流程.md`，以后直接问你或者翻文件都能找到。\n\n几个关键点我自己标记一下：\n- **尺寸重量是生死线** — 运费算不明白基本白干\n- **有单量再谈价** — 谈判优先级高于纠结进价那几毛钱\n- **抄两类款** — 成熟卖家新品 + 新卖家出单款，比自己瞎猜稳多了\n\n你们现在主攻哪个站点？马来还是菲律宾？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1315,"output":140,"cacheRead":16003,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":17458,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778127432020,"responseId":"064b4548823a876334d16c1598b9d901"}}
